[ch (id=null) [title Absence of Value]

    To encode the absence of value (aka [c null], [c nil], [c void], [c nothing], etc. in programming languages) you use a [link (url="^[get core_spec_url]#tagged_leaf_node") tagged leaf node] (i.e. a tagged node without child nodes):
    [code
        """
        [remark]
        """
    ]

    JSON version:
    [code
        """
        {"remark": null}
        """
    ]
]
